'''Giant lobsters''' are encountered during the [[The Slug Menace|Slug Menace]] quest in [[Witchaven Dungeon]]. They are aggressive to all players, even to those more than twice their combat level. After the quest is complete, they can no longer be found in the dungeon.

Giant lobsters which cannot be fought are also seen on the [[Fishing Platform]].

